      "solution": "\nx_1, y_1, w_1, h_1 = map(int, input().split())\nx_2, y_2, w_2, h_2 = map(int, input().split())\n\nif (x_1 >= x_2 + w_2) or (x_1 + w_1 <= x_2) or (y_1 + h_1 <= y_2) or (y_1 >= y_2 + h_2):\n    print(0)\nelse:\n    area1 = w_1 * h_1\n    area2 = w_2 * h_2\n    \n    intersection = (min(x_1 + w_1, x_2 + w_2) - max(x_1, x_2)) * (min(y_1 + h_1, y_2 + h_2) - max(y_1, y_2))\n    union = area1 + area2 - intersection\n\n    iou = intersection / union\n\n    print(int(iou) if int(iou) == iou else iou)",
